@startuml BaseLayer Workflow

!theme crt-amber

title BaseLayer - Code Flow and Actions

participant "Application" as app
participant "BaseLayer" as base
participant "AppState" as state

== Initialization ==
app -> base: AddLayer<BaseLayer>(app, z_index)
base -> base: OnAdd()
base --> app: Layer added

== Render Loop ==
app -> base: OnIterate()
base -> state: Get application state
state --> base: State reference
base --> app: Iteration done

app -> base: OnRender()
base -> base: Render base UI elements
base --> app: Rendering done

== Cleanup ==
app -> base: OnRemove()
base --> app: Cleanup complete

@enduml
